OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to text scam plot of
OL,4,CTube passengers
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to plotting
OL,7,Fto target Tube passengers in a text
OL,8,Fmessage scam using homemade "SMS
OL,9,Fblasters" hidden inside suitcases.
OL,11,FUnsuspecting London Underground
OL,12,Ftravellers who walked past the
OL,13,Fsuitcases received fake messages about
OL,14,Fa failed parcel delivery and a link
OL,15,Finviting them input their details to
OL,16,Fsort the problem, but the aim was
OL,17,Freally to "plunder their bank
OL,18,Faccounts," the prosecution said.
