OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to text scam plot of
OL,4,CTube passengers
OL,6,FOn Friday, the fifth day of his trial
OL,7,Fat Inner London Crown Court, Daoyan
OL,8,FShang, 20, changed his plea to a
OL,9,Fcharge of conspiracy to defraud
OL,10,Fbetween January and March 2025 to
OL,11,Fguilty.
OL,13,FIt came a day after "top boss" Zhijia
OL,14,FFan, 48, also changed his plea to
OL,15,Fguilty on the same charge.
OL,17,FThe jury, upon the direction of the
OL,18,Fjudge, returned a guilty verdict
OL,19,Fagainst Shang and was then dismissed.
