OL,6,FThe scam is known as "smishing", a
OL,7,Fcombination of SMS and phishing, where
OL,8,Ffraudsters try to get people to reveal
OL,9,Fpersonal information by duping them
OL,10,Finto thinking they are from a
OL,11,Freputable company.
OL,13,FRecorder Alex Stein told the jury:
OL,14,F"Sometimes in these courts it is when
OL,15,Feveryone is in the same room and the
OL,16,Fstrength of the prosecution evidence
OL,17,Fis spelled out that the defendants see
OL,18,Fthe strength of the case against them
OL,19,F` that has been the case."
