OL,6,FThe prosecution said it is not
OL,7,Fpressing ahead with a further charge
OL,8,Fof possessing an article for use in
OL,9,Ffraud against Fan and Shang, who was
OL,10,Fdescribed as his "right-hand man" in
OL,11,Fthe smishing gang.
OL,13,FBoth men, of no fixed abodes, are to
OL,14,Fbe sentenced on Tuesday along with two
OL,15,Fother defendants.
OL,17,FWan Hafiz, 41, of no fixed abode,
OL,18,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fconspiracy to defraud and possession
OL,20,Fof articles for use in fraud.
