OL,6,FProsecutor Alex Davidson had told
OL,7,Fjurors in Fan and Shang's trials: "The
OL,8,Fprosecution say that these two
OL,9,Findividuals were part of a crime group
OL,10,Fwho, early last year, wheeled around
OL,11,Fdevices in suitcases ` known as SMS
OL,12,Fblasters ` (that is a) short message
OL,13,Fservice or text message ` on the
OL,14,FLondon Underground which sent scam
OL,15,Fmessages to passengers' phones,
OL,16,Fpretending to be from Evri and Royal
OL,17,FMail."
