OL,4,CTube passengers
OL,6,FHe added: "Phone numbers are targeted
OL,7,Fand fraudulent text messages are
OL,8,Fbroadcast, using a rather
OL,9,Fsophisticated device, which is adapted
OL,10,Ffor the sole purpose of defrauding the
OL,11,Fpublic."
OL,13,FHe described the SMS blaster as a
OL,14,F"crude" device that worked by
OL,15,F"masquerading as a legitimate cell
OL,16,Ftower, tricking nearby phones into
OL,17,Fconnecting to it instead of their
OL,18,Fnormal network" and "once a phone
OL,19,Fconnects to the SMS blaster,
OL,20,Ffraudulent messages are sent with
OL,21,Flinks to fraudulent websites".
